  "bugs":[
    {
      "description":"IE 9, 10 and 11 do not support rem units when used in the \"line-height\" property when used on :before and :after pseudo elements (https://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedback/details/776744)."
    },
    {
      "description":"Borders sized in \"rem\" disappear when the page is zoomed out in Chrome."
    },
    {
      "description":"Reportedly does not work on Android 4.3 browser for Samsung Note II or the Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 on Android 4.2."
    },
    {
      "description":"Chrome 31-34 & Chrome-based Android versions (like 4.4) [have a font size bug](https://code.google.com/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=319623) that occurs when the root element has a percentage-based size."
    },
    {
      "description":"Causes content display and scrolling issues on iPhone 4 which typically has Safari 5.1."
    }
